  rdfs:comment           "Entity Regulation Rule 3. The relation 'JAK2 phosphorylates VAV1 in EPO:p-8Y-EPOR:p-12Y-JAK2:LYN:IRS2:p-Y-CRKL:RASGEF1:p-Y-SHC1:GRB2:VAV1' 'null' 'EPO:phospho-EPOR:phospho-JAK2:LYN:IRS2:phospho-CRKL:RAPGEF1:GRB2-1:SOS1,phospho-VAV1 mediates exchange of GTP for GDP bound to RAS' was inferred because:\n reaction1 has an output that is the enabler of reaction 2." , "Imported from Reactome: https://reactome.org/content/detail/R-HSA-9027284" ;
